Job_Description:
Designing and developing IAM (Security) solutions which consist of quarterly security access reviews (for Financially Significant Applications), validations (Employees and Contractors of the organization), deployments (Profile based access requests provisioning and de provisioning), enhancements, reporting & dashboards support activities and monitoring - information security, enterprise identity and access management (Security) system leveraging the Identity and Access Management platform;
Performing technical aspects of Identity and access management; (Cyber Security) platform implementation, across different phases including Architecture, Design, Implementation / Realization, Unit Testing, System Integration Testing, User Acceptance Testing, Production Rollouts, and Post-Production Support;
Configuring of code in support of all components of the Identity Access Governance solution, OKTA Cloud, and Privileged Access Management. This ranges from workflows to adapters, firewalls, network zones, OVA appliance setup, database integration, authentication (LDAP/Okta), security policies and system configuration; design, implement and support release/deployment Management processes.

United States - Arizona - Phoenix

